# Netlify Redirects Configuration for Rosehill Security
# Redirects from rosehillsecurity.com AND rosehilldefence.com to security.rosehill.group

# Force old domains to new subdomain - rosehillsecurity.com
https://rosehillsecurity.com/* https://security.rosehill.group/:splat 301!
http://rosehillsecurity.com/* https://security.rosehill.group/:splat 301!
https://www.rosehillsecurity.com/* https://security.rosehill.group/:splat 301!
http://www.rosehillsecurity.com/* https://security.rosehill.group/:splat 301!

# Force old domains to new subdomain - rosehilldefence.com
https://rosehilldefence.com/* https://security.rosehill.group/:splat 301!
http://rosehilldefence.com/* https://security.rosehill.group/:splat 301!
https://www.rosehilldefence.com/* https://security.rosehill.group/:splat 301!
http://www.rosehilldefence.com/* https://security.rosehill.group/:splat 301!

# Force HTTPS
http://security.rosehill.group/* https://security.rosehill.group/:splat 301!

